text: Galina Yenyukhina (born 1 October 1959) is a Russian former cyclist. She competed in the women's sprint at the 1992 Summer Olympics for the Unified Team. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Unified Team Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Krasnoyarsk
